snippet.title: The Amber Heard case is far from solved! Is she getting away with this?
snippet.description:
Golden Heard claimed in a British court on Wednesday that ex Johnny Depp tossed "30 or thereabouts bottles" at her as though they were "projectiles or bombs" during a plastered and exciting attack in Australia in March 2015 that additionally saw him inadvertently cut off a piece of his finger. Taking the observer box for a third day at the High Court in London during Depp's criticism of evidence against a British newspaper, the entertainer invalidated his claim that it was she who blew her top and that she had harmed him.
